# ── Local operating docs ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# Working AI/operating state, kept local by default. Only the root-level files
# below are ignored; durable, shareable docs (README.md, CHANGELOG.md,
# DECISIONS.md, docs/) stay tracked. To version-control these instead, set
# "Operating docs tracking: tracked" in INIT.md and delete this block.
/AGENTS.md
/CONTEXT.md
/MEMORY.md
/BACKLOGS.md
/HANDOFF.md
# Legacy rootsator <=0.4 projects may still have TODO.md; keep it local if present.
/TODO.md
/CHECKLIST.md
/WORKLOG.md
/SPEC.md
/REQUIREMENTS.md
/LESSONS.md
/TESTS.md
*.local.md

# ── Private material and credentials ────────────────────────────────────
# Containment beats guessing: keep ANYTHING sensitive inside one of these
# ignored directories. Then the rest of the project can be fully git-tracked
# without enumerating secret filenames. Do NOT add broad filename globs such as
# *token* or *secret* or *.key — they also hide normal source (tokenizer.c,
# Keynote .key files, etc.).
*_private/
*_internal/
secrets/

# Environment files are the one common in-place secret; commit a template instead.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
!.env.sample

# ── Cold planning history and generated output ──────────────────────────
docs/plans/active/*.md
docs/plans/archive/*.md
!docs/plans/active/README.md
!docs/plans/archive/README.md
build/
app/build/
.gradle/
.idea/
local.properties
*.apk
*.aab
resources/prep/
resources/cache/

# ── Common local noise ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
*.tmp
*.log
